{"tid":493045,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"窮人自棄手冊（香港版）","createTime":"2017-12-08T06:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T07:17:29.000Z","uid":123335,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c8fb737966ac22b241dd7e134c46621902585ca0","tid":493045,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:47:01.000Z","msg":"有冇窮巴窮絲已經想放棄脫貧？<br />\n因為脫貧需要花需大量既精力，心力，<br />\n亦唔一定成功<br />\n我都明白，有時真係會心灰意冷，打算放棄<br />\n<br />\n但其實，<br />\n有冇諗過做窮人都可以好精彩？<br />\n<br />\n以下我有D Tips 俾大家<br />\n如知生活係貧窮線下，依然活得精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">衣著: </span></ins><br />\n-主要以U記, G2000 買衫為主<br />\n-副以一個Lv or 同等品牌既銀包 (非常耐用) <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>食:</ins></span><br />\n-主要自己煮, 仲可以享受廚藝既樂趣<br />\n-可以間中飲下咖啡, 茶, 朱古力呢D 會令心情振奮幸福既食物 <br />\n-間中買醉, 短暫向現實說Bye <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>住: </ins></span><br />\n-同屋企住, 家人過世就繼續住 <br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">行: </span></ins><br />\n-長期著跑鞋, 路程短就跑/行過去, 順便做埋運動, 增加血液循環, 有保健作用"},{"pid":"f6408932931ff3fdfd23e837fa7f0d73e18ff49c","tid":493045,"uid":123335,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:52:08.000Z","msg":"<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其他增加幸福感既方法: </span></ins><br />\n- 多做運動, 最好係團體運動, 因為運動會增加身體既幸福荷爾蒙 (e.g. 血清素, 內啡肽, 多巴胺) <br />\n而團體活動亦會更加加強多巴胺既分泌 <br />\n<br />\n-多親密既Social , 建立多D密友關係。因為要從Social 中獲得幸福，秘訣係要重質不重量，有知心既好友，女友，家庭關係，大家會拎個心出黎互相Care , <br />\n呢份溫暖係有錢都買唔到<br />\n<br />\n-睡眠: 訓夠7-8hr , 會有幸福感"},{"pid":"0b4f650fbcc16785aa1f9a260bcc8c2816c37757","tid":493045,"uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:53:50.000Z","msg":"只要大家努力自棄脫貧<br />\n試一試我D Tips <br />\n窮人都一樣可以活得精彩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0609581d1f73ddff8349dc50d7d1c4f832069eae","tid":493045,"uid":14377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1c94a2e0da7748f9f82794be94b59a78515454","tid":493045,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc54c2f9181de9afff8307d30fe6b2c52a0b377","tid":493045,"uid":39215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:00:58.000Z","msg":"我依家攞住老綜 <br />\n望住班人晨咁早趕番工<br />\n真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a35dd9a773a8496a69a362c2a7a308d28e28f15","tid":493045,"uid":159246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:02:59.000Z","msg":"吊， 幾同意， 因為我都咁做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.."},{"pid":"e73368ea413e831dd41d3169ebea15ba71bdfdc4","tid":493045,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:06:38.000Z","msg":"窮撚拎LV銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39dffd3e556d943e11f2bfae30c4525f4219c633","tid":493045,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:12:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮撚拎LV銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為真係好耐用<br />\n除返使用年數，唔會貴得過你買5,6舊水果d 銀包"},{"pid":"7858cf983bfba3455e2f02dd84b22e6f9c5347d3","tid":493045,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:17:29.000Z","msg":"我用緊嗰個百幾蚊，仲要係朋友送<br />\n買得起5，6百蚊以上一個銀包都唔窮啦<br />\n仲要買LV，有幾窮呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}